- Makefile:

automatically generate header prerequisites:

see: https://www.gnu.org/software/make/manual/html_node/Automatic-Prerequisites.html


- xcompile: clean up Docker host
	- set relevant environment variables
	- configure for 32 and 64 bit ARM
	- create mechanism to mount deps:
		- wiringpi
		- libroyale
		- unfolding projet
	  as external volumes automatically


